            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1636549652406-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>pastry</strong> with the <strong>galette filling</strong>, leaving a 2cm border</p><p>Fold the pastry border over the edge of the filling</p><p>Tip: Start from one corner and work around in one direction, overlapping the pastry each time</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to make multiple galettes</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
